{"tid":2378820,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：政府果斷決定封區　不會對受影響居民作賠償","createTime":"2021-01-24T20:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T20:07:37.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5273e5e546e02f4dd24b7bedeb95e8acc80dfa97","tid":2378820,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T20:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/truthmediahk/posts/3688545894546238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftruthmediahk%2Fposts%2F3688545894546238&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCOxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=75bc9216\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/truthmediahk/posts/3688545894546238</a><br />\n<br />\n【張建宗：政府果斷決定封區 不會對受影響居民作賠償】<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗今早到佐敦封鎖區視察後見記者，他指政府知道措施會為當區居民構成不變，惟當局不會作出賠償，希望居民體諒。<br />\n<br />\n張重申，本次封區行動決定果斷，當局將總結經驗，不排除未來會在其他地區展開類似行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/11DrziH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F11DrziH.png&h=baedb1e5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}